	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not sure if this is the correct forum, but anyway.. The "Super Mario 25th anniversary" for Wii has recently been released if you haven't noticed.
<br />There's an included booklet which contains photos of the development-sketches (for example level-data) of "Super Mario Bros" for NES, which are really inspiring and cool to look at. 
<br />Just wanted to let you know.. <img src="./images/smilies/icon_smile.gif" alt=":)" title="Smile" />

		

		</td>
	</tr>
